metadata.name: Togetherness
metadata.description:
Artist: Diana Junakovic  
Title: Togetherness  
Edition: Open

There is enough room in the world for all of us, we can share this water, this sky, these stones. Although we are all different, we are still equal. Like a branching river, we can open the paths to our hearts. Let's embrace peace and grow together in love.

I wanted to make my work more accessible to all my friends who have shown me love and support for the last 10 months and for anyone who resonates with my work.
